title: Match of the Day 2014-05-12 720p 50fps x264-wAm.mkv
description:
SPORT: Match of the Day
On: BBC 1 HD
Date: Saturday 12th April 2014

Gary Lineker presents highlights of the day's six Premier League games. Fulham take on fellow strugglers Norwich looking to maintain their 100% winning record against the Canaries at Craven Cottage in the Premier League. Not only have the Cottagers won all three previous meetings but they have scored 13 goals in the process. Cardiff travel to Southampton seeking their first win away to the Saints since 1962, Sunderland welcome Everton to the Stadium of Light having beaten them 1-0 in their last two league meetings, and West Brom host Tottenham, a side they have not beaten in their last six attempts. Elsewhere, Crystal Palace entertain Aston Villa at Selhurst Park defending a four-match unbeaten home streak against them and Newcastle travel to Stoke, having beaten the Potters in four of their last five games.
